dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. "394831ID 6-11." "794828AI 6-11." "794834AI (G03398) 6-11." "794833AI (G03397) 6-11." "794829Ai (G01117) 6-11." "794830AI (G00046) 6-11." "794831AI (G00046) 6-11." "794832AI (G00046) 6-11." Includes a chronicle of major historical events since 1900 to the present, text, comparative area map, location map. Ancillary maps: Golan Heights -- Oil and gas infrastructure -- Population density -- Ethnoreligious distribution. Shows provincial boundaries, four classes of roads, railroads, ports, and other features, "Boundary representation is not necessarily authoritative." "Some population based on estimates."
